headline: NetApp Appoints Frank Pelzer to the Board of Directors
summary: SAN JOSE, Calif., March 26, 2025--NetApp® (NASDAQ: NTAP), the intelligent data infrastructure company, today announced that Frank Pelzer, Chief Operating Officer at Spotnana, has joined its Board of Directors. This brings the number of directors on the NetApp Board of Directors to ten, nine of whom are independent and 40% of whom have been appointed within the last five years.
